<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q12_v10" title="Q12_v10" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>
      En una reunión se registró la asistencia de la siguiente manera:<br />
      Personas ausentes: <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math><br />
      Personas presentes: (no se indica)<br />
      Personas citadas en total: <m:math><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math>
    </p>
    <p>
      ¿Qué porcentaje de las personas citadas asistió a la reunión?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>Elige la alternativa que completa correctamente el registro anterior.</qti-prompt>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">12,5%<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si fueron citadas <m:math><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math> personas y hubo <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math> ausentes, entonces las presentes fueron <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. El porcentaje de asistencia es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> = <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> ≈ <m:math><m:mn>11,1</m:mn></m:math>%. Por lo tanto, <m:math><m:mn>12,5</m:mn></m:math>% no corresponde.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">11,1%<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Si en total fueron citadas <m:math><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math> personas y <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math> estuvieron ausentes, entonces asistió <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> persona. El porcentaje de asistencia es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> = <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> ≈ <m:math><m:mn>11,1</m:mn></m:math>%.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">80%<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Con <m:math><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math> personas citadas y <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math> ausentes, las presentes son <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Entonces la asistencia es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> ≈ <m:math><m:mn>11,1</m:mn></m:math>%. Además, <m:math><m:mn>80</m:mn></m:math>% de <m:math><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math> es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,8</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>7,2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, y eso no coincide con <m:math><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:math> persona asistente.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">88,8%<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si hubo <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math> ausentes de un total de <m:math><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math>, entonces asistió solo <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> persona. El porcentaje de asistencia es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> ≈ <m:math><m:mn>11,1</m:mn></m:math>%. En cambio, <m:math><m:mn>88,8</m:mn></m:math>% corresponde aproximadamente a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>%, que no es la asistencia, sino casi la proporción de ausentes.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar los datos</strong></p>
            <p>Se sabe que hubo <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math> personas ausentes y que en total fueron citadas <m:math><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math> personas.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Calcular cuántas personas asistieron</strong></p>
            <p>Las personas presentes se obtienen restando las ausentes al total:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Entonces asistió <m:math><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:math> persona.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Escribir la fracción de asistencia</strong></p>
            <p>La fracción de personas que asistió es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Convertir la fracción a porcentaje</strong></p>
            <p>Para obtener el porcentaje, se multiplica por <m:math><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Y <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> ≈ <m:math><m:mn>11,1</m:mn></m:math>%.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El porcentaje de las personas citadas que asistió a la reunión fue <strong><m:math><m:mn>11,1</m:mn></m:math>%</strong>.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>